article.description: — Mate Okros scored 20 points to help Drexel defeat Hampton 99-65 on Monday in a Coastal Athletic Association opener for both teams.
article.headline: Okros scores 20, Drexel defeats Hampton 99-65 in Coastal Athletic Association opener
article.linkText: Okros scores 20, Drexel defeats Hampton 99-65 in Coastal Athletic Association opener
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Mate Okros scored 20 points to help Drexel defeat Hampton 99-65 on Monday in a Coastal Athletic Association opener for both teams. Okros was 6 of 9 shooting, including 4 for 7 from 3-point range, and went 4 for 4 from the line for the Dragons (8-6). Amari Williams scored 16 points while shooting 5 of 6 from the field and 6 for 7 from the line, and added six rebounds. Kobe Magee shot 5 for 8, including 2 for 4 from beyond the arc to finish with 12 points. Jordan Nesbitt led the Pirates (4-9) in scoring, finishing with 12 points and four assists. Hampton also got 12 points from Tristan Maxwell. In addition, Kyrese Mullen had 11 points and 13 rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
